The paper deals with detecting vulnerabilities in regular expressions, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also presents a static analysis technique, which is a common topic in software engineering (cs.SE). Regular expressions are often implemented using programming languages, making the paper relevant to programming languages (cs.PL).
